"Editor\\``. For details instructions on debugging OpenShot on Windows, "
"please see `this wiki <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/Windows-"
"Debugging-with-GDB>`_."
msgstr ""
"在附加除錯器之前，請下載 OpenShot 的**最新版本** ： https://www.openshot.org/"
"download#daily。將此版本安裝到預設位置：``C:\\Program Files\\OpenShot Video "
"Editor\\`` 。有關在 Windows 上除錯 OpenShot 的詳細說明，請參閱 ` 此維基 "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/Windows-Debugging-with-"
"GDB>`_ 。 `this wiki <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/Windows-"
"Debugging-with-GDB>`_"

